================================================================================
Third-party components
================================================================================

This product includes data sourced from LiteLLM by BerriAI:

  https://github.com/BerriAI/litellm
  Copyright (c) BerriAI
  Licensed under the MIT License.

Specifically, the file
  litellm-core/src/main/resources/model_prices_and_context_window.json
is a snapshot of the model price and context window table maintained in
the LiteLLM repository, used here under the terms of LiteLLM's MIT License.

The Java implementations of the SDK, Router and Proxy in this repository
are an independent re-implementation; no source code from LiteLLM was
copied. The OpenAI-compatible REST endpoint shapes, `config.yaml` schema
and management API conventions are interface designs that are
intentionally aligned with LiteLLM's, but interface designs are not
subject to copyright protection.
